Multiple aftershocks jolted the area after the 7 . 0 magnitude quake took place , the largest aftershock in magnitude being the 5 . 1 - magnitude one which shook the bordering area of Lushan and Baoxing counties of Sichuan at 8 : 07 a . m .. Till the time of release , several aftershocks rated above 4 . 0 - magnitude hit the area , including a M - 4 . 8 quake at 8 : 06 a . m , a M - 4 . 6 one at 9 : 02 a . m , a M - 4 . 1 one at 8 : 31 a . m ., and a M - 4 . 1 on at 8 : 37 .